{"title_page": "List of Brooklyn Nine-Nine characters", "text_new": "{{short description|Characters on American television series Brooklyn Nine-Nine}}\n{{Use American English|date=August 2019}}\n\n''[[Brooklyn Nine-Nine]]'' is an American sitcom which premiered in September 2013 on [[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]], and was later recommissioned by [[NBC]]. The show revolves around the [[Detective#United States|detective squad]] of the [[fiction]]al 99th Precinct of the [[New York Police Department]], located in [[Brooklyn]].\n\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Brooklyn Nine-Nine'' characters}}{{TOC limit|3}}\n\n== Cast ==\n=== Main ===\n<!-- Please do not change the layout of the following table without first discussing it on the talk page and reaching consensus to do so. -->\n<onlyinclude>{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Character\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Actor\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Rank\n! colspan=\"7\" |Seasons\n|-\n! style=\"width: 8%;\" | [[Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 1)|1]]\n! style=\"width: 8%;\" | [[Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 2)|2]]\n! style=\"width: 8%;\" | [[Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 3)|3]]\n! style=\"width: 8%;\" | [[Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 4)|4]]\n! style=\"width: 8%;\" | [[Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 5)|5]]\n! style=\"width: 8%;\" | [[Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 6)|6]]\n! style=\"width: 8%;\" | [[Brooklyn Nine-Nine (season 7)|7]]\n|-\n| [[#Jake Peralta|Jake Peralta]] || [[Andy Samberg]] || align=\"center\"| Detective || colspan=\"7\" {{cMain}}\n|-\n| [[#Rosa Diaz|Rosa Diaz]] || [[Stephanie Beatriz]] || align=\"center\"| Detective || colspan=\"7\" {{cMain|Main}}\n|-\n| [[#Terry Jeffords|Terry Jeffords]] || [[Terry Crews]] || align=\"center\"| Detective Sergeant (1\u20136)<br />Lieutenant (6\u2013present) || colspan=\"7\" {{cMain|Main}}\n|-\n| [[#Amy Santiago|Amy Santiago]] || [[Melissa Fumero]] || align=\"center\"| Detective (1\u20135)<br />Sergeant (5\u2013present) || colspan=\"7\" {{cMain|Main}}\n|-\n| [[#Charles Boyle|Charles Boyle]] || [[Joe Lo Truglio]] || 